Bridgeway









EST 1993
STATISTICALLY DRIVEN,
EVIDENCE-BASED INVESTING
Bridgeway is driven by two fundamental beliefs that separate it from most of Wall Street.
First and foremost, we care.  We care about putting investors first.  We care about performance, integrity, and the world at large. Second, we believe a great philosophy is only valuable when it’s applied to the real world…with execution and results.
LEARN MORE		








		EVIDENCE-BASED INVESTING PROVIDES INVESTORS WITH REPEATABLE SOLUTIONS


			Bridgeway strives to be the investment manager of choice among institutional investors and financial advisors who share our passion for evidence, data, and logic in reaching investment decisions.


At Bridgeway, we seek to provide investment building blocks mutual funds, separate accounts, and sub-advisory services to a select group of investors. We are the first to say, “Bridgeway is not for everyone.” We look for clients whose investment goals fit our unique expertise: delivering investment solutions that are statistically driven and grounded in academic theory. We take our fiduciary responsibilities very seriously and put our clients first. All Bridgeway partners are encouraged to invest in Bridgeway Strategies.

 




		Statistically driven, evidence-based equity investment manager

Experienced team focused on client needs and innovative solutionsFounded in 1993$7.7 Billion in firm assets under management as of 12/31/201628 Partners (permanent staff) 
