Sub-advised - Bridgeway 








































Bridgeway










SUB-ADVISORY SERVICES
ESTABLISHED PRODUCTS, STRONG RELATIONSHIPS







SUB-ADVISORY SERVICES – ESTABLISHED PRODUCTS, STRONG RELATIONSHIPS
In addition to our separate account strategies, Bridgeway lends its investment expertise to sub-advisory relationships with institutional investors and other asset management firms. Our portfolio managers and analysts are readily available to our sub-advisory clients.Take advantage of the cost-effective and convenient method of adding to your fund offerings by using our sub-advisory services instead of expending the time and effort of building your own funds. You will receive the same disciplined, evidence-based investment process available to our separate account clients. 




Contact



FOR MORE INFORMATION ABOUT OUR SUB-ADVISORY SERVICES, PLEASE CONTACT US AT 713-661-3500 EXT. 1.




 




